title: 85. Taran Tactical - The Michael Sartain Podcast
description:
Taran Butler ( IG: @Tarantactical ) is world class professional shooter and gunsmith. He’s a 15 time USPSA national champion. He’s the 1st ever multi gun triple crown champion and the last ever combat master champion. He’s the owner of @TaranTactical Innovations in Simi Valley. He’s also the creator of the Pit Viper featured in the movie John Wick 4.
